display.title: Rocket Fuel
description: Rocket Fuel mostly exists for compatibility with other mods. You'll love it if you're making your own pack.
As an actual fuel for GTCEu generators? Terrible!
In this modpack, &&aRocket Fuel&&r is required to obtain &&dNether Stars&&r.
Automating it may be a big hit to your resources, but you can safely batch craft using an overclocked &&3Large Chemical Reactor&&r.
